reviews.review_text: Credit where credit is due A very special thanks goes out to Barry B. for supplying (and trusting) me with his 1st Gen Cassettes.
Brent's birthday I was at this show, one of the best one's I ever went to!!!!!!!!!!  RIP BRENT

Listen to the river sing sweet songs... An excellent recording of a very fine show from the 1988 six show Sunbelt tour.
This just has that certain something that puts a show over the top.
